comments: Strus (CLE) extends his arm into Maxey's (PHI) chest and the contact affects his SQBR during his drive to the basket.
Mitchell (CLE) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Garland (CLE) reaches in and initiates contact with Maxey's (PHI) left arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Bamba (PHI) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Mitchell (CLE) makes hand on ball contact as Hield (PHI) gathers the ball at the end of his drive.
LeVert (CLE) makes contact with the ball and deflects the entry pass to Maxey (PHI) prior to incidental body contact occurring.
Levert (CLE) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Strus (CLE) and Bamba (PHI) mutually engage and disengage during the throw-in.
Hield (PHI) initiates contact with Mitchell's (CLE) arm, which affects his SQBR during his driving shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) reaches across Maxey's (PHI) arms and initiates contact to Maxey's wrist which affects his driving shot attempt.
Strus (CLE) makes contact with the ball and dislodges the ball away from Oubre Jr. (PHI) prior to incidental arm contact occurring during his layup attempt.
Allen (CLE) initiates contact with Council IV's (PHI) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Council IV (PHI) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Allen (CLE) is already in Council IV's (PHI) path and briefly grasps Council IV's shoulder before correcting.
Reed (PHI) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact initiated by Mitchell (CLE) before making clean contact with the ball.

Allen (CLE) places a hand on Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) back while he is airborne contesting the shot attempt at the basket, but the contact is marginal.  When Oubre Jr. returns to the floor he steps on a teammate's foot, which causes him to trip.
Mitchell (CLE) plants his right foot in bounds before making contact with the loose ball.
